            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " the right to strike as a fundamental right of workers.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "callout",
        "calloutEmoji": "üí°",
        "calloutText": "Follow us on <a href=\"https://apple.news/TeRci1RtoQfWCNA5h7NTBlg\">Apple News</a> and <a href=\"https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMPvKngswktW2Aw\">Google News</a> to make sure you see our stories first, and to help make sure others see our breaking news as well.",
        "backgroundColor": "grey"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "On August 17, an emergency board Biden convened on the labor negotiations ",
